channel.title: 525 need help 525 (rsdw)
channel.description:
Hello, im DemonWars owner of RuneScape Demon Wars 508. And i am planning on adding a 525 version of the server, but to do that i need help with running the server: i'll explain.
i have downloaded multiple 525 servers and clients but every time i run both the server and client i get this error: [code]Error_Game_js5connect[/code] while i have never had this error with a other version like: 317,474,508,562,602 and 614 so only with the 525 version.
So if some1 knows how to fix this, or knows the correct 525 cache please reply with either the link or a solution, i would be very happy and i will make you a Admin on the 525 version.
[shadow=red,left]Greetings: DemonWars[/shadow]
